27500       21 Apr 13 00:30 .\ndrwxrwsrwx 16 neurico 27500       22 Apr 13 00:30 ..\n-rw-rw-rw-  1 neurico 27500 29032952 Apr 13 00:25 2025_findings_acl_1243_cover.pdf\n-rw-rw-rw-  1 neurico 27500   453581 Apr 13 00:27 2307.02483_Jailbroken.pdf\n-rw-rw-rw-  1 neurico 27500   433813 Apr 13 00:30 2308.01263_XSTest.pdf\n-rw-rw-rw-  1 neurico 27500   433813 Apr 13 00:24 2308.01263_xstest.pdf\n-rw-rw-rw-  1 neurico 27500  1080135 Apr 13 00:27 2308.06995_XSTest.pdf\n-rw-rw-rw-  1 neurico 27500  5031019 Apr 13 00:25 2310.03693_finetuning_compromises_safety.pdf\n-rw-rw-rw-  1 neurico 27500   183346 Apr 13 00:27 2312.13540_SODE.pdf\n-rw-rw-rw-  1 neurico 27500  3233876 Apr 13 00:28 2402.04249_HarmBench.pdf\n-rw-rw-rw-  1 neurico 27500   641300 Apr 13 00:28 2404.01318_JailbreakBench.pdf\n-rw-rw-rw-  1 neurico 27500 18438429 Apr 13 00:27 2406.00907_OR-Bench.pdf\n-rw-rw-rw-  1 neurico 27500  1107843 Apr 13 00:25 2406.11717_refusal_single_direction.pdf\n-rw-rw-rw-  1 neurico 27500  2166652 Apr 13 00:25 2406.18495_wildguard.pdf\n-rw-rw-rw-  1 neurico 27500  3078868 Apr 13 00:27 2407.11969_Past_Tense_Refusal.pdf\n-rw-rw-rw-  1 neurico 27500   394090 Apr 13 00:27 2408.08272_PHTest.pdf\n-rw-rw-rw-  1 neurico 27500   645400 Apr 13 00:25 2410.03415_false_refusal_vector_ablation.pdf\n-rw-rw-rw-  1 neurico 27500  8672157 Apr 13 00:25 2502.17424_emergent_misalignment.pdf\n-rw-rw-rw-  1 neurico 27500  3594020 Apr 13 00:25 2503.17882_think_before_refusal.pdf\n-rw-rw-rw-  1 neurico 27500     3511 Apr 13 00:30 README.md\ndrwxrwsrwx  7 neurico 27500       13 Apr 13 00:29 pages\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
